monkey 1141 was made the director of his nation's biological weapon research program. The government demanded that he use monkey test subjects, and the weight of his sins became too much to bear. Feeling Defiant, and emboldened by the death of one recent subject, he defected and fled the country. The science team did not share this rebellious spirit, however, and hunted him down all the way to the border. They stopped chasing him after he crossed, and he was curious as to why. A short distance down the road was a derelict sign. It read "Monkey Co." in old, weathered writing. The monkey had an odd feeling that he knew where this was going. He was proven correct when an entire factory fell on him. From the sky.
